{"tid":1704182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【九龍塘】血濺又一城！瘋警追打市民落電梯險釀人踩人","createTime":"2019-11-10T15:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T15:11:35.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c7c1d9a9376ef916fe87ed6a520dc340b5e511a","tid":1704182,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:01:24.000Z","msg":"【八區開花●九龍塘】血濺又一城！瘋警追打市民落電梯險釀人踩人<br />\n<br />\n商場變戰場！逆權抗爭5個月，香港人與暴政周旋進入新形態，由以往街頭遊行，改進入商場巷戰，冷氣開放、窗明几淨的shopping mall變成抗暴陣地，早前有科大男生疑因警方清場墮樓失救亡，令局勢再升溫，今日（10日）再有市民在多區示威。而在九龍塘又一城商場，有穿着黑色衫的示威者，於商場內針對部份商店破壞。有一批便衣警員喬裝成示威者，混入市民當中，並以警棍襲擊示威者，觸發雙方打鬥。有示威者被打至頭破血流，但在場警員不容義務急救員上前為受傷示威者治理。<br />\n<br />\n其後數百名蒙面防暴警進入商場內增援，到場後不斷驅趕在場人士，並在沒有衝擊之下，多次舉槍指嚇圍觀的市民，嚇壞很多一家大細。有市民在扶手電梯向下離開時，多個防暴警上前用警棍追打，當時扶手電梯仍然運作，險釀人踩人，險象環生。防暴警又不斷舉起胡椒噴劑，攻擊正後退的市民、急救員和記者。<br />\n<br />\n及後所有市民及記者，都被防暴警趕至LG層，記者無法到較上層，拍攝被防暴警制服的示威者，是否被警察暴力毆打。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191110/60251774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191110%2F60251774&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=47cf0c75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191110%2F60251774&h=b40f1a6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191110/60251774</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RikKo2si48Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRikKo2si48Y&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=c2d75234\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RikKo2si48Y</a>"},{"pid":"6483c0a8d16931d9d2200556d80c134d56523abe","tid":1704182,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jM9yEVS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjM9yEVS.gif&h=36baf129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"798185b6d56c03c6fe9df241466dd706e501f2bf","tid":1704182,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:01:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d98dbd56654c9c870ae14f9d267039f18af24db","tid":1704182,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/HKIP2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKIP2&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=04c7dae3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HKIP2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ws9KMEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fws9KMEO.jpg&h=ae373530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Hong Kong Independence Party <br />\n5 agendas </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(1)  UK has the mandate from the People of Hong Kong to annul the Sino-British Joint Declaration right away; Also should the US subsequently abolish the HK Policy Act.<br />\n<br />\n(2) the UK and the US governments are requested by the Hongkongers for taking on the PRC&rsquo;s illegal occupation of Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n(3)  We require the United Kingdom to enforce those three unterminated treaties over Hong Kong sovereignty ( the Treaty of Nanking; the Convention of Peking; the Second Convention of Peking ).<br />\n<br />\n(4) We demand Anglo-American or Nato joint military base in Hong Kong on a permanent basis, the expense of which will be covered by ourselves!<br />\n<br />\n(5) Hong Kong should and is going to be an independent Commonwealth nation.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/HKIP2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKIP2&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=04c7dae3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HKIP2</a>"},{"pid":"195c2318b1e6f8ab406b699beeceb97450cc7471","tid":1704182,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:03:42.000Z","msg":"&quot;網傳又一城有示威者死亡....&quot;...???"},{"pid":"783e1cc58b655cc24c8df78b900c3408f073b66f","tid":1704182,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/CmyrFgR.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"dd98296dbaa02623aaf6cf42387d5a1a25550198","tid":1704182,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:06:13.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"192ef364ff969aaf8966431809583aedf497ca92","tid":1704182,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:09:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/attackonnews/posts/2471383819856116/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fattackonnews%2Fposts%2F2471383819856116%2F&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=4f9b4ca3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/attackonnews/posts/2471383819856116/</a>"},{"pid":"d7c93f0fc358509b0bf1ce677de31744b6f5bc04","tid":1704182,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123d1fcd310327cda8bfeda1db11a249329ec13b","tid":1704182,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:10:51.000Z","msg":"想問下阻人喐手嘅左膠去咗邊？"},{"pid":"6dab1e1ebe77a5fd38c0578a7c7d189495e4ead2","tid":1704182,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:11:35.000Z","msg":"似公安"}]}